            <div class="container">
                <div class="row ">
                    <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center pt-3">
                        <div class="col-5">

                            <h4> A note from the restaurant</h4>
                            <p>
                                Age restrictions apply. Because the bar sells alcoholic beverages and allows the use of tobacco products, state law prohibits entry to persons under 18 years of age.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-2"></div>
                        <div class="col-5 ">
                            <h4> Important dining information</h4>
                            <p>
                                We have a 20 minute grace period. Please call us if you are running later than 20 minutes after your booked time.

                                We may contact you about this booking, so please ensure your email.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container-fluid ">
            <div class="ak-booking-system-map-from">
